snippet.title: Guitar Hero Live  - Win The Crowd Trailer | PS4, PS3
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/guitar-hero-live-ps4/

Lenny Kravitz and James Franco take each other on in GH Live, the new mode that features real crowds with real reactions. Only available in the all-new Guitar Hero Live. Coming October 20th, 2015.

http://www.guitarhero.com
